text: Jeannot Robitaille is a archer from Canada. Robitaille competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. He was born on 19 April 1953.Jeannot Robitaille == References == Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian archers Category:Olympians for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Quebec
